Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.05,0:42:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Tidak
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.43,0:42:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Aku bukan iblis
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.78,0:42:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Aku bukan iblis
